vxap-downloader (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Multi-threaded HTTP/HTTPS/FTP download engine (libcurl)
  * BitTorrent support via libtorrent-rasterbar 2.x
  * Glassmorphism GTK4 UI with live dashboard
  * Browser extension with native messaging (Chrome/Firefox)
  * Clipboard monitoring for URL auto-detection
  * SQLite download history database

 -- VAXP Team <team@vaxp.org>  Sat, 01 Mar 2026 01:00:00 +0300

